column2: "This is a strange structure, I wonder what it's for."
"I have no idea. I've never set foot around this area."
"And you're the ones here to investigate, not me."
"That's true, but this is your native planet. You have no idea what this is?"
"For someone born on this planet, you really don't know much about here at all do you?"
"You could say that, but I don't even know if I was born on this planet to begin with."
"No one remembers what happens where they're born. Do you remember?"
"You don't think anything happened to you that you don't remember?"
"This conversation gives me the creeps. But I can't deny the possibility..."
"Maybe the fact that we can understand each other means we were born in the same place."
"How rude can you be? And seriously learn to take a joke."
